  "detailed_description": "GORN is a ludicrously violent VR gladiator simulator, made by Free Lives, the developers of Broforce and Genital Jousting. Featuring a unique, fully physics driven combat engine, GORN combatants will be able to creatively execute their most violent gladiatorial fantasies in virtual reality. Savagely strike down an infinite supply of poorly-animated opponents with all manner of weapons – from swords, maces, and bows to nunchuks, throwing knives, massive two-handed warhammers or even your blood-soaked bare hands. The only limits to the carnage are your imagination and decency, in the most brutal and savage VR face-smashing game ever produced by man.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578620/extras/9cd2df5584b3d75eed0b6774f65e35c6.poster.avif?t=1740671868\" width=420 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578620/extras/9cd2df5584b3d75eed0b6774f65e35c6.webm?t=1740671868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/578620/extras/9cd2df5584b3d75eed0b6774f65e35c6.mp4?t=1740671868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
